    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: #ffffff;\">Added</h3>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41298\">​</a><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-36999\">LCD-36999</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </span>- Display commit's author avatar on build list:</strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span> </span>Now the avatar of the commit's author who generated a specific build will be shown on the build list instead of a system image everytime Jenkins is involved in the build process. Giving more clarity to the team and streamlining discussions and knowledge sharing.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span>\n</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-42379\">LCD-42379</a></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span> </span>- Provide access to commonly used features on the services popover:</strong><span> </span>Now it's easier to access the logs, the monitoring page or the shell of a specific service. No need to click and apply filters anymore. From the overview page's popover you can jump straight to the information you want! </span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: #ffffff;\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-43837\">LCD-43837</a><span> </span>- Deploy app from marketplace bug:<span> </span></strong>Fixed an issue where certain apps bought in marketplace were unable to be deployed even though they were correctly purchased.</li>\n<li>\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44127\">LCD-44127</a> <span>and <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-43717\">LCD-43717</a> </span>- Bugs on the storage usage representation and its relation to backup size:<span> </span></strong>Fixed issues where the value shown in the Plan&amp;Usage page visualization for storage was not matching doclib backups, not accounting for certain items, and outright not being shown to some users.</li>\n</ul>"
      },
